# Playwright Runner Rules

This project is for authorized automation only.

Rules:
- Do not bypass CAPTCHA, MFA, bot detection, or protected login flows.
- Use manual/protected-login handoff for blocked login pages.
- Never log secrets, passwords, tokens, cookies, or session values.
- Keep runner changes backward compatible with existing saved flows/workflows when possible.
- For runner/orchestrator changes, run `npm run verify:runner`.
- For recorder changes, run the relevant recorder verification script if available.
